status_srv

status_srv.pl : A perl server that takes text information over a socket
 and writes it to a web page. Normally runs on blade16. The webpage 
location is  declared in status_srv.cfg


status_client.pl :  A perl script that takes standard input and sends it to the status_srv using a socket. Normally runs on quest16

status_srv.cfg  :  configuration file read by both of the above programs

